::Prowl/Striker/Ramulus/Smokescreen/Ramhorn::

Prowl ducks, half the shots from Ares hitting him. He growls, firing back at 
the newcomer.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Striker jumps out of the way of Hades, firing at him.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus runs into the battlefield, firing at Shuko.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Smokescreen sits down behind a rock. Taking out two guns, he jumps out from 
behind the boulder, firing at Serpentor.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramhorn takes out a charge, throwing it at Anubis.
